const Formitems = [
  {
    cName : 'form-group',
    labelfor : 'fname',
    labeltitle : 'First Name:',
    inputtype : 'text',
    inputcName : 'form-control',
    placeholder : 'Enter Your First Name',
    name : 'fname'
  },
  {
    cName : 'form-group',
    labelfor : 'lname',
    labeltitle : 'Last Name:',
    inputtype : 'text',
    inputcName : 'form-control',
    placeholder : 'Enter Your Last Name',
    name : 'lname'
  },
  {
    cName : 'form-group',
    labelfor : 'email',
    labeltitle : 'Email:',
    inputtype : 'email',
    inputcName : 'form-control',
    placeholder : 'Enter Your Email',
    name : 'email'
  }
]
 export default Formitems
